cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with the problem of 6D object pose estimation from images, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method involves the use of a deep neural network for direct regression of 6D poses, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper also discusses the performance of the proposed method in terms of accuracy and speed, which could be relevant to the graphics (cs.GR) community.
